{"tid":1742590,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"馬鞍山燒人案疑犯僅被控擾亂秩序","createTime":"2019-11-21T00:37:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T07:18:45.000Z","uid":283285,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"873ae56d1ab77b566b7e5ad08eef940e30a79705","tid":1742590,"uid":283285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T00:37:40.000Z","msg":"<strong>馬鞍山淋潑懷疑易燃液體點火案兩人被控擾亂秩序今提堂</strong><br />\n<br />\n馬鞍山上星期有人被淋潑懷疑易燃液體並點火的案件，被捕的33歲姓陳女子，及39歲姓鄺男子，已各被暫控一項公眾地方作出擾亂秩序行為罪，案件今日上午在東區裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n案發在上星期一中午過後，警方接獲途人報案，指出一名57歲男子，在鞍駿街一條行人天橋與他人爭執，其後有人向該名男子淋潑懷疑易燃液體並點火，之後逃去。該名男子身體多處燒傷。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">33同39歲 你話我多心都好 我地手足年紀有咁老咩？<br />\n唔控襲擊同傷人 控擾亂秩序？？？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有人想入我地數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"7d812a7fa0fed15f875518d870e6fa2d14c5f569","tid":1742590,"uid":69650,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T00:39:52.000Z","msg":"都捉唔到個犯"},{"pid":"5a7bacc53c5daafb1c701ce40b9f29f16afcc12a","tid":1742590,"uid":6845,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T00:40:10.000Z","msg":"又割"},{"pid":"28f1cfae81ac52fb3d60a063950321f1d88d460e","tid":1742590,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T00:40:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba73bdfb0073aca802b0f3cda1f7597520f5017","tid":1742590,"uid":11208,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T00:40:53.000Z","msg":"宜兩個係汁邊講粗口炸"},{"pid":"f9204fba94220562576ff232ccc535c466539a8a","tid":1742590,"uid":55043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T00:40:57.000Z","msg":"呢兩個手足好似係出黎屌狗<br />\n<br />\n換句話說姐係另類辱警罪"},{"pid":"f5e2cffb04714230e448f3f56c5adcfe